text:
(1) A general view, northwest from the Municipal Building, at the intersection of Park Row and Centre Street, showing a portion of the New Jersey Shore, and the Hudson River on the left, and the Empire State Building, (34th St and Fifth Ave), on the right.

May 3, 1932.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) The same, a year later, from a different angle and not showing the Empire State Building.

June 23, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.
title: General view - Centre Street - Northwest.
